{
  "texts": [
    "Bouteraa et al.",
    "27 developed a feature-based decision support system based on cascading fuzzy logic algorithms to measure the degree of pain in wrist fracture patients in exercise sessions of VRehab and control an exercise rehabilitation robot accordingly.",
    "In addition to visual movement data collected through RGB and depth cameras, various time-domain and frequencydomain features were extracted from current and electromyography sensors on the robot.",
    "The extracted features were input to cascades of fuzzy logic algorithms to output the degree of pain.",
    "Fang et al."
  ]
}